How To Heal Your Gut

Process: 

With CLEAN hands:

Chop 1 Red Cabbage
Sprinkle Celtic sea salt on top
Massage the cabbage until juicy (2 min)
Transfer to a mason jar 
Fill with filtered water (be sure it covers the cabbage)
Cover with lid and let sit out for 7 days
After 7 days refrigerate 

Enjoy!
